#: _posts/2025-03-13-gemini-personal-assistant.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Security Considerations"
msgstr "安全考虑因素"

#: _posts/2025-03-13-gemini-personal-assistant.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "We have dealt with several important security considerations."
msgstr "我们已经解决了几个重要的安全问题。"

#: _posts/2025-03-13-gemini-personal-assistant.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The obvious consideration is that you do not want to allow unauthenticated "
"access to LLM which works with the sensitve data. It is common sense and not "
"specific to the AI security domain."
msgstr "一个显而易见的考虑因素是，您不希望允许未经验证的访问处理敏感数据的 LLM。这是常识，并非人工智能安全领域所特有。"

#: _posts/2025-03-13-gemini-personal-assistant.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The tricker issue is how to prevent LLM making mistakes when calling tools "
"with side-effects. For example, if you look at the Google Calendar REST API "
"client tool which allows to modify the event, you will note the `calendarId` "
"parameter - the agent finds the id of a specific calendar from the list of "
"calendars. How can the user be protected from the event beng moved to the "
"wrong calendar ?"
msgstr ""
"更棘手的问题是如何防止 LLM 在调用具有副作用的工具时出错。例如，如果查看允许修改事件的 Google Calendar REST API "
"客户端工具，就会注意到 `calendarId` 参数--代理会从日历列表中查找特定日历的 id。如何防止用户将事件移动到错误的日历上？"

#: _posts/2025-03-13-gemini-personal-assistant.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The https://github.com/quarkiverse/quarkus-langchain4j[Quarkus LangChain4j] "
"team is looking at various options such as guardrails and hallucination "
"strategies for tools."
msgstr ""
"link:https://github.com/quarkiverse/quarkus-langchain4j[Quarkus LangChain4j] "
"团队正在研究各种方案，如防护栏和工具的幻觉策略。"

#: _posts/2025-03-13-gemini-personal-assistant.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You can also have your tool do the checks before making an actual call. For "
"example, instead of having a declarative REST client tool that can update "
"calendars, have a Tool bean which injects Google Calendar REST client and "
"enforces that a calendar update event call is allowed only if it is "
"`PersonalAssistant` calendar which is about to be updated."
msgstr ""
"您还可以让工具在实际调用前进行检查。例如，与其使用一个可更新日历的声明式 REST 客户端工具，不如使用一个注入 Google Calendar "
"REST 客户端的 Tool Bean，只有在 `PersonalAssistant` 日历即将更新时才允许日历更新事件调用。"

#: _posts/2025-03-13-gemini-personal-assistant.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"As far as the actual chat-bot implementation is concerned, ensuring a secure "
"WebSockets HTTP upgrade is critical but it is complicated by the fact that "
"JavaScript WebSockets API does not enforce the same origin requirement. "
"Nonetheless, using a technique such as a custom ticketing system, combined "
"with using a secure `wss:` scheme can help to minimize risks. Look at the "
"https://github.com/quarkiverse/quarkus-langchain4j/tree/main/samples/secure-"
"sql-chatbot[secure-sql-chatbot] demo in the https://github.com/quarkiverse/"
"quarkus-langchain4j[Quarkus LangChain4j] repository for more details."
msgstr ""
"就实际的聊天机器人实施而言，确保安全的 WebSockets HTTP 升级至关重要，但 JavaScript WebSockets API "
"并不强制执行相同的起源要求，这使得实施变得复杂。不过，使用自定义票务系统等技术，结合使用安全的 `wss:` "
"方案，可以帮助将风险降至最低。更多详情，请查看 link:https://github.com/quarkiverse/quarkus-"
"langchain4j[Quarkus LangChain4j] 存储库中的 link:https://github.com/quarkiverse/"
"quarkus-langchain4j/tree/main/samples/secure-sql-chatbot[secure-sql-chatbot] "
"演示。"

#: _posts/2025-03-13-gemini-personal-assistant.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Please note that using WebSockets is not a pre-requisite for implementing a "
